Green Scale: 30-50Kpp<br>
<br>
The prices are from AB.<br>
AB is a European splitserver from all the older US servers and alot of highlevels moved, so its prices are all messed up.<br>
<br>
The problem is still that the supply of the green scale is very limited, though, so alot of warriors move past the epic and get better weapons instead.<br>
These warriors just finish their epic quest when they are uber in gear and can take Hoshkar in a few seconds.<br>
The epic quest is to these guys just another high level quest and more a status symbol, than a weapon.<br>
